    <h1>CAN-SPAM Act</h1>
    <p class="description">The US federal law governing commercial email. Sets rules for headers, subject lines, opt-outs, and physical addresses — with penalties up to <strong>$53,088 per email</strong>.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
          <span class="meta-author-role">Marketing Head · theStacc</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-divider"></div>
      <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-label">Published</span><span class="meta-value">Jun 2026</span></div>
      <div class="meta-divider"></div>
